    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it still even smells like a new car! I've babied this thing since day one, always kept it garaged, and the paint is literally flawless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
