    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians at scheduled intervals. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been pampered with an obsessive attention to detail. All original manuals, two sets of keys, and service receipts are included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
